Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來硬讓她說呣啾真是太正確了gowasu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好軟啊zamasu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗議的時候反而更可愛了gesu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣啾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 要什麼我都給你喔gesu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣啾呣啾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 你要幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣啾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕啊gowasu
