Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都走到這一步已經無法回頭了gesu反而
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是真冬的gesu喔 反而
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小真冬的gesu也很讚啊gesu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這局面已經一發不可收了啊zamasu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣～啾!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知弦姐站起來了gesu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣啾啾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐著的時候是挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來就像是雪人了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呣啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好超現實
